title: Incoming Mr High Energy
description: Incoming Mr High Energy Manhua A hundred years after the Cataclysm, a completely new profession was born. They controlled iron, copper, phosphorus, gold, silicon, carbon……At the start he immolated the female lead to the heavens, Gao Neng saw his own hidden gifts, and was frozen in shock: iron 100%, copper 100%, tin 100%, silver 100%, gold 100%, phosphorus 100%, sulphur 100%, silicon 100%…… High Energy Strikes High-Energy Strikes Incoming Mr High Energy 高能来袭 Gao Neng Strikes
